        <Parent_String>rings (finger jewelry) [300046012], jewelry worn on arms and hands [300209288], jewelry by location [300211901], jewelry [300209286], worn costume accessories [300209274], costume accessories [300209273], costume (mode of fashion) [300178802], Costume (hierarchy name) [300209261], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
